<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 08:09:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴基斯坦信德省因绑架印度教女孩爆发抗议活动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/protests-erupt-in-pakistans-dera-murad-jamali-over-abduction-of-hindu-girl-named-priya-kumari/articleshow/108961662.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108961662.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德拉穆拉德贾马里的印度教社区成员和商人走上街头，抗议最近绑架一名名叫普里亚·库玛丽的年轻女孩，并要求立即采取行动，确保她安全返回。抗议者批评信德省政府没有采取有效措施寻找和营救几天前在苏库尔被绑架的普里亚。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:28:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/protests-erupt-in-pakistans-dera-murad-jamali-over-abduction-of-hindu-girl-named-priya-kumari/articleshow/108961662.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦国防部长对人民院选举后改善与新德里的双边关系持乐观态度</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-defence-minister-optimistic-of-improving-bilateral-ties-with-new-delhi-post-lok-sabha-elections/articleshow/108961729.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108961729.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦国防部长卡瓦贾·阿西夫预计，尽管存在恐怖主义指控、关系紧张以及联合国大会决议，但印度大选后巴印关系将得到改善。他讨论了各种挑战和解决方案，旨在更好地双边合作。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 05:33:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-defence-minister-optimistic-of-improving-bilateral-ties-with-new-delhi-post-lok-sabha-elections/articleshow/108961729.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度裔美国议员寻求有关针对印度教徒的仇恨犯罪增加的简报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/indian-american-lawmakers-seek-briefing-on-rise-in-hate-crimes-against-hindus-in-us/articleshow/108961134.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108961134.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五名印裔美国议员要求美国司法部和联邦调查局就针对印度教徒的仇恨犯罪和破坏寺庙行为的增加提供情况通报。人们对缺乏嫌疑人线索表示担忧，强调执法协调和联邦监督对平等保护的重视。共同努力旨在打击针对印度教徒的仇恨犯罪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:09:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/indian-american-lawmakers-seek-briefing-on-rise-in-hate-crimes-against-hindus-in-us/articleshow/108961134.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯谴责以色列袭击伊朗领事馆</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-condemns-israeli-attack-on-iranian-consulate/articleshow/108963697.cms</link><description>俄罗斯谴责以色列袭击伊朗驻叙利亚领事馆，并呼吁这个犹太国家停止这种“完全不可接受”的行为。周一，疑似以色列战机轰炸了伊朗驻叙利亚大使馆，伊朗称此次袭击造成七名军事顾问死亡，其中包括三名高级指挥官，标志着以色列与其地区对手的战争大幅升级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 05:43:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-condemns-israeli-attack-on-iranian-consulate/articleshow/108963697.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击伊朗驻大马士革大使馆附属建筑 造成8人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/8-killed-as-israel-strikes-iran-embassy-annex-in-damascus/articleshow/108963536.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108963536.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 05:35:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/8-killed-as-israel-strikes-iran-embassy-annex-in-damascus/articleshow/108963536.cms</guid></item><item><title>法官拒绝驳回针对亨特·拜登的税务案件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/judge-refuses-to-toss-out-tax-case-against-hunter-biden/articleshow/108960089.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108960089.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;斯卡西法官否认了亨特·拜登税务案件中的驳回动议，驳回了政治动机的指控。该案由特别检察官戴维·韦斯（David Weiss）负责监督，其中包括与逃税和谎报联邦表格购买枪支有关的指控。亨特对在洛杉矶提起的九项重罪和轻罪税务犯罪表示无罪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/judge-refuses-to-toss-out-tax-case-against-hunter-biden/articleshow/108960089.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯媒体办公室称，以色列对加沙的空袭导致外国援助人员死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-airstrike-on-gaza-kills-foreign-aid-workers-hamas-run-media-office-says/articleshow/108960022.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108960022.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯控制的加沙政府媒体办公室周一晚间表示，包括外国人在内的世界中央厨房员工在以色列对加沙的空袭中惨遭杀害。加沙中部代尔巴拉赫事件中的遇难者包括波兰、澳大利亚和英国公民，以及一名巴勒斯坦人，这引起了哈马斯、以色列军方、澳大利亚政府和人道主义援助组织的回应。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 03:16:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-airstrike-on-gaza-kills-foreign-aid-workers-hamas-run-media-office-says/articleshow/108960022.cms</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩真主党称以色列对叙利亚的袭击将受到“惩罚”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanons-hezbollah-says-israel-strike-in-syria-will-get-punishment/articleshow/108958981.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108958981.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;真主党警告以色列将对在叙利亚大马士革杀害伊斯兰革命卫队的行为进行报复。以色列的空袭造成七名伊斯兰革命卫队成员死亡，其中包括准将穆罕默德·礼萨·扎赫迪和另一名高级军官。真主党支持加沙的哈马斯。以色列表示不会对报道的袭击事件发表评论，但伊朗誓言要对袭击进行报复。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 03:13:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanons-hezbollah-says-israel-strike-in-syria-will-get-punishment/articleshow/108958981.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普支付 1.75 亿美元保释金以避免资产被扣押</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-pays-175-million-bond-to-avert-asset-seizure/articleshow/108958910.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108958910.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;今年 2 月，法官对唐纳德·特朗普处以 4.54 亿美元的罚款，原因是他在资产方面存在欺骗行为，以获取优惠的贷款条件。本周一，曼哈顿一家上诉法院接受了特朗普缴纳的保证金，在他的上诉悬而未决期间停止了处罚的执行。在今年 11 月的白宫竞选中，如果上诉失败，特朗普将面临罚款和额外利息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 02:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-pays-175-million-bond-to-avert-asset-seizure/articleshow/108958910.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么巴基斯坦与恐怖分子的幽会会自食其果</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/why-pakistans-tryst-with-terror-is-boomeranging/articleshow/108958101.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108958101.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦受到来自阿富汗境内活动的塔利班组织（TTP）的攻击。萨钦·帕拉沙尔分析了这个问题及其对新德里和伊斯兰堡的影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 00:56:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/why-pakistans-tryst-with-terror-is-boomeranging/articleshow/108958101.cms</guid></item><item><title>佛罗里达州最高法院允许选民投票表决堕胎权</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/florida-top-court-lets-abortion-rights-ballot-measure-go-to-voters/articleshow/108955525.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108955525.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;该提案的支持者在一月份获得了将其列入选票所需的签名数量。它将禁止“根据患者的医疗保健提供者的决定，禁止、惩罚、延迟或限制在生存之前或在必要时保护患者健康的堕胎”的法律。根据共和党州长 Ron DeSantis 于 2022 年签署的一项法律，佛罗里达州 15 周后堕胎是非法的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 22:44:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/florida-top-court-lets-abortion-rights-ballot-measure-go-to-voters/articleshow/108955525.cms</guid></item><item><title>毛茸茸的拖鞋和运动裤：中国年轻人在工作中拥抱“粗俗服装”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/furry-slippers-and-sweatpants-young-chinese-embrace-gross-outfits-at-work/articleshow/108953965.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108953965.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国年轻工人在社交媒体上掀起“工作中的粗俗着装”运动，反抗传统的工作着装规范，引发了一场关于“平躺”生活方式和拒绝雄心壮志的社会辩论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:09:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/furry-slippers-and-sweatpants-young-chinese-embrace-gross-outfits-at-work/articleshow/108953965.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦最高法院将审理“三军情报局干涉司法事务”案件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-supreme-court-to-hear-case-about-isi-interference-in-judicial-matters/articleshow/108953959.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108953959.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-supreme-court-to-hear-case-about-isi-interference-in-judicial-matters/articleshow/108953959.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国首相里希·苏纳克因将无家可归者定为犯罪的法案而面临党内反对</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-pm-rishi-sunak-faces-revolt-from-party-over-bill-to-criminalise-homelessness/articleshow/108953931.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108953931.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克因将无家可归者定为刑事犯罪而遭到保守党议员的强烈反对。苏埃拉·布雷弗曼的法案面临反对，保守党在即将到来的竞选活动中与反在职情绪作斗争。 PTI 报道了这一情况。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-pm-rishi-sunak-faces-revolt-from-party-over-bill-to-criminalise-homelessness/articleshow/108953931.cms</guid></item><item><title>法院在托沙卡纳案中暂缓伊姆兰·汗和妻子的监禁，但他们不会被释放</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/court-suspends-jail-term-for-imran-khan-wife-in-toshakhana-case-but-they-wont-be-freed/articleshow/108953893.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108953893.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;高等法院表示，托沙卡纳的判决将继续缓刑，直到 10 天后开始的开斋节假期结束后对伊姆兰的上诉案件做出裁决。 “没有证据支持这一定罪，”伊姆兰的律师阿里·扎法尔周一告诉记者，并解释了为何最高委员会在上诉第一次听证会上暂停了判决。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:56:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/court-suspends-jail-term-for-imran-khan-wife-in-toshakhana-case-but-they-wont-be-freed/articleshow/108953893.cms</guid></item><item><title>官员称，巴基斯坦逮捕了针对中国人的恐怖袭击主谋和另外 12 人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-arrests-mastermind-12-others-for-terror-attack-on-chinese-say-officials/articleshow/108953842.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108953842.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;开伯尔-普赫图赫瓦省反恐部门（CTD）对此次袭击事件展开调查，并将此次袭击归咎于被禁止的巴基斯坦塔利班运动（TTP）。没有任何组织声称对这起恐怖袭击事件负责。当时，中国工兵从伊斯兰堡前往位于该省上科希斯坦地区总部达苏的营地，一名自杀式炸弹袭击者将装有爆炸物的汽车撞向他们。上拉区碧沙姆地区的车辆。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:46:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-arrests-mastermind-12-others-for-terror-attack-on-chinese-say-officials/articleshow/108953842.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗大马士革领事馆部分被夷为平地，高级将领在空袭中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/part-of-irans-damascus-consulate-flattened-top-general-killed-in-air-raid/articleshow/108953779.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108953779.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列对大马士革的空袭造成穆罕默德·礼萨·扎赫迪将军死亡，伊朗外交部长对此予以谴责。这次袭击的目标是与巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织领导人的会面。叙利亚和伊朗国家通讯社报道了人员伤亡。以色列军方拒绝对这次袭击发表评论，但四名不愿透露姓名的以色列官员承认，以色列实施了这次袭击，目标是扎赫迪。他们没有证实他已被杀。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/part-of-irans-damascus-consulate-flattened-top-general-killed-in-air-raid/articleshow/108953779.cms</guid></item><item><title>谁是伊朗革命卫队？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-are-irans-revolutionary-guards/articleshow/108953780.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108953780.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队于 1979 年革命后成立，保护什叶派文书制度。它拥有125,000名人员，其中包括巴斯基民兵和圣城旅。美国将其列为恐怖组织，并监管重要的弹道导弹计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:35:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-are-irans-revolutionary-guards/articleshow/108953780.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准关闭外国新闻频道的法案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-approves-bill-to-shut-down-foreign-news-channels/articleshow/108951582.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108951582.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-approves-bill-to-shut-down-foreign-news-channels/articleshow/108951582.cms</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，伊朗卫队指挥官在以色列袭击大马士革领事馆中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-guards-commander-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-consulate-in-damascus-source-says/articleshow/108951537.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108951537.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:42:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-guards-commander-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-consulate-in-damascus-source-says/articleshow/108951537.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>